es"," significant"," funding"," from"," business"," and"," industry",","," which"," enables"," it"," to"," provide"," research"," grants",","," fellowships",","," and"," publishing"," support"," to"," its"," members","."," In"," addition"," to"," its"," research"," activities",","," the"," Royal"," Institute"," also"," runs"," various"," public"," events"," and"," lectures"," which"," are"," open"," to"," the"," public","."," Lectures"," and"," workshops"," hosted"," by"," RI"," members"," cover"," a"," broad"," range"," of"," topics"," such"," as"," architecture",","," the"," environment",","," health"," and"," medicine",","," law",","," education"," and"," politics","."," The"," RI"," also"," hosts"," various"," public"," conferences"," and"," seminars",","," which"," explore"," issues"," at"," the"," intersection"," of"," science"," and"," society","."," The"," Royal"," Institute"," is"," an"," independent"," organisation"," whose"," mission"," is"," to"," promote"," research"," and"," knowledge"," in"," the"," sciences"," and"," humanities","."," Through"," its"," wide"," range"," of"," activities",","," the"," RI"," encourages"," thoughtful"," dialogue"," between"," academics",","," researchers"," and"," experts"," from"," across"," disciplines","."," This"," dialogue"," has"," the"," potential"," to"," inform"," and"," advance"," debates"," on"," complex"," social"," issues",","," as"," well"," as"," to"," make"," policy"," recommendations"," to"," government"," bodies"," and"," industry","."],"sub_source":"wikipedia","model":"davinci","label":1}